--- !u!114 &1636835082
MonoBehaviour:
  m_ObjectHideFlags: 0
  m_CorrespondingSourceObject: {fileID: 0}
  m_PrefabInstance: {fileID: 0}
  m_PrefabAsset: {fileID: 0}
  m_GameObject: {fileID: 1636835080}
  m_Enabled: 1
  m_EditorHideFlags: 0
  m_Script: {fileID: 11500000, guid: b83a42f8f29be63479ff24c6194bf230, type: 3}
  m_Name: 
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: Assembly-CSharp::SimpleDialogue
  conversation:
  - text: "Yine ayn\u0131 so\u011Fuk\u2026 ayn\u0131 ta\u015F duvarlar\u2026\nKa\xE7
      y\u0131ld\u0131r buraday\u0131z Rua? Art\u0131k saymay\u0131 bile b\u0131rakt\u0131m."
    portrait: {fileID: 6630341104690361922, guid: 80791bcba4d49424a99f4ca6ea31c45d, type: 3}
    speakerName: Akina
  - text: "Saymay\u0131 b\u0131rak\u0131rsan umudu da b\u0131rak\u0131rs\u0131n."
    portrait: {fileID: -1336964543194316448, guid: dcacd733b0d473047a392186bc43b1f6, type: 3}
    speakerName: Rua
  - text: "Belki de umut diye bir \u015Fey yoktur.\n\u015Eu da\u011Flara bak\u2026
      Demir gibi sertler. Buradan kimse \xE7\u0131kamaz."
    portrait: {fileID: 6630341104690361922, guid: 80791bcba4d49424a99f4ca6ea31c45d, type: 3}
    speakerName: Akina
  - text: "Atalar\u0131m\u0131z sava\u015Flardan \xE7\u0131kt\u0131. A\xE7l\u0131ktan
      \xE7\u0131kt\u0131.\nBir da\u011F m\u0131 durduracak bizi?"
    portrait: {fileID: -1336964543194316448, guid: dcacd733b0d473047a392186bc43b1f6, type: 3}
    speakerName: Rua
  - text: "Bu sadece da\u011F de\u011Fil Rua\u2026 Bu bizim kaderimiz.\n\u0130nsanlar
      korkuyor. \xC7ocuklar a\xE7. Herkes t\xFCkenmi\u015F durumda."
    portrait: {fileID: 6630341104690361922, guid: 80791bcba4d49424a99f4ca6ea31c45d, type: 3}
    speakerName: Akina
  - text: "Tam da bu y\xFCzden birinin aya\u011Fa kalkmas\u0131 gerekiyor."
    portrait: {fileID: -1336964543194316448, guid: dcacd733b0d473047a392186bc43b1f6, type: 3}
    speakerName: Rua
  - text: "Sen yine o kahramanl\u0131k hik\xE2yelerini d\xFC\u015F\xFCn\xFCyorsun\u2026"
    portrait: {fileID: 6630341104690361922, guid: 80791bcba4d49424a99f4ca6ea31c45d, type: 3}
    speakerName: Akina
  - text: "Hik\xE2ye de\u011Fil. G\xF6rev.\nE\u011Fer \xE7\u0131k\u0131\u015F varsa
      onu bulaca\u011F\u0131m."
    portrait: {fileID: -1336964543194316448, guid: dcacd733b0d473047a392186bc43b1f6, type: 3}
    speakerName: Rua
  - text: "Tek ba\u015F\u0131na m\u0131?"
    portrait: {fileID: 6630341104690361922, guid: 80791bcba4d49424a99f4ca6ea31c45d, type: 3}
    speakerName: Akina
  - text: Gerekirse evet.
    portrait: {fileID: -1336964543194316448, guid: dcacd733b0d473047a392186bc43b1f6, type: 3}
    speakerName: Rua
  - text: "Ya d\xF6nemezsen?"
    portrait: {fileID: 6630341104690361922, guid: 80791bcba4d49424a99f4ca6ea31c45d, type: 3}
    speakerName: Akina
  - text: "O zaman en az\u0131ndan denemi\u015F olurum. Ama burada beklersek zaten
      kaybetmi\u015F olaca\u011F\u0131z."
    portrait: {fileID: -1336964543194316448, guid: dcacd733b0d473047a392186bc43b1f6, type: 3}
    speakerName: Rua
  - text: "Ben korkunun lideri olmayaca\u011F\u0131m Akina. \u0130nsanlara yeniden
      umut g\xF6sterece\u011Fim."
    portrait: {fileID: -1336964543194316448, guid: dcacd733b0d473047a392186bc43b1f6, type: 3}
    speakerName: Rua
  - text: "Sen ger\xE7ekten d\u0131\u015Far\u0131da bir yol oldu\u011Funa inan\u0131yor
      musun?"
    portrait: {fileID: 6630341104690361922, guid: 80791bcba4d49424a99f4ca6ea31c45d, type: 3}
    speakerName: Akina
  - text: "\u0130nan\u0131yorum. Ve e\u011Fer o yolu bulursam\u2026 Ergenekon sadece
      bir hapishane de\u011Fil, yeniden do\u011Fu\u015Fumuz olacak."
    portrait: {fileID: -1336964543194316448, guid: dcacd733b0d473047a392186bc43b1f6, type: 3}
    speakerName: Rua
  - text: "\u2026Belki sen delisin Rua. "
    portrait: {fileID: 6630341104690361922, guid: 80791bcba4d49424a99f4ca6ea31c45d, type: 3}
    speakerName: Akina
  - text: "Belki de halk\u0131 kurtarmak i\xE7in biraz deli olmak gerekir."
    portrait: {fileID: -1336964543194316448, guid: dcacd733b0d473047a392186bc43b1f6, type: 3}
    speakerName: Rua
  onDialogueEnd:
    m_PersistentCalls:
      m_Calls:
      - m_Target: {fileID: 11500000, guid: 9e99be48b3760d84894aa273e9020853, type: 3}
        m_TargetAssemblyTypeName: SimpleDialogue, Assembly-CSharp
        m_MethodName: 
        m_Mode: 1
        m_Arguments:
          m_ObjectArgument: {fileID: 0}
          m_ObjectArgumentAssemblyTypeName: UnityEngine.Object, UnityEngine
          m_IntArgument: 0
          m_FloatArgument: 0
          m_StringArgument: 
          m_BoolArgument: 0
        m_CallState: 0
